					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5154820#post-3701491</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5154820/scp-3136#post-3701491</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2018 14:53:09 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Stallmantic</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3472766</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Sorry if this ruins the mystique of it, but I correlated the hardness of the writing utensil to the texture of the instance. For instance, the pen would create a chitinous shell, and a thicker one with the black marker, but something like the crayon creates an instance with a furry exterior, if that makes any sense. Also, thank you for the positive feedback!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5154820#post-3699760</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
