					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5154820#post-3699493</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5154820/scp-3136#post-3699493</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2018 12:14:12 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>PeppersGhost</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1553042</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The idea that the Foundation would repeatedly test an anomaly that creates <em>straight-up sea monsters</em> is pretty dubious. That said, though, you've explored the concept in a really fun way, and there are a lot of nice little touches throughout. Consider my disbelief suspended. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
